  "nodes": [
    {
      "id": "3682f30e-32a7-4a1b-83dc-ba09f3a829ce",
      "name": "Sticky Note 78894ee7",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        160,
        120
      ],
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Fluxo 2 — Checkout Event\n\n**Trigger:** POST /webhook/checkout-event\n\n**Payload esperado:**\n```json\n{\n  \"email\": \"...\",\n  \"product_name\": \"nome exato do produto\",\n  \"transaction_id\": \"TXN123\",\n  \"amount\": 197.00,\n  \"payment_method\": \"pix|boleto|cartao_credito|outro\",\n  \"installments\": 1,\n  \"platform\": \"hotmart|pepper|assiny\",\n  \"occurred_at\": \"2025-01-15T10:30:00Z\"\n}\n```\n\n**O que faz:**\n1. Busca lead_id pelo email\n2. Busca product_id pelo nome\n3. Insere checkout_event (ignora se transaction_id ja existe)\n4. Atualiza status do lead para comprador",
        "color": 4,
        "width": 1120,
        "height": 400
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "4311a0fe-6e45-4ffb-bb7a-2720dbabd9fe",
      "name": "Webhook Checkout Event",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.webhook",
      "typeVersion": 2.1,
      "position": [
        240,
        300
      ],
      "parameters": {
        "httpMethod": "POST",
        "path": "checkout-event",
        "responseMode": "onReceived"
      },
      "webhookId": "7463380d-1e54-4aea-a445-699a60cb979b"
    },
    {
      "id": "0493984a-23f5-427c-876b-f69c6b72610c",
      "name": "Normalizar Checkout",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.set",
      "typeVersion": 3.4,
      "position": [
        500,
        300
      ],
      "parameters": {
        "mode": "raw",
        "jsonOutput": "={{ { \"email\": ($json.body.email || \"\").trim().toLowerCase(), \"product_name\": $json.body.product_name || null, \"transaction_id\": $json.body.transaction_id || null, \"amount_cents\": $json.body.amount ? Math.round($json.body.amount * 100) : null, \"payment_method\": $json.body.payment_method || \"outro\", \"installments\": $json.body.installments || 1, \"platform\": $json.body.platform || null, \"utm_source\": $json.body.utm_source || null, \"utm_medium\": $json.body.utm_medium || null, \"utm_campaign\": $json.body.utm_campaign || null, \"utm_content\": $json.body.utm_content || null, \"utm_term\": $json.body.utm_term || null, \"occurred_at\": $json.body.occurred_at || $now.toISO() } }}"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "a326663a-a8d3-421c-a103-d0827b3b001b",
      "name": "Buscar Lead por Email",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest",
      "typeVersion": 4.4,
      "position": [
        760,
        300
      ],
      "parameters": {
        "method": "GET",
        "url": "https://yscegbszuckpdcopdszj.supabase.co/rest/v1/leads",
        "authentication": "genericCredentialType",
        "genericAuthType": "httpHeaderAuth",
        "sendQuery": true,
        "queryParameters": {
          "parameters": [
            {
              "name": "email",
              "value": "=eq.{{ $json.email }}"
            },
            {
              "name": "select",
              "value": "id,email"
            },
            {
              "name": "limit",
              "value": "1"
            }
          ]
        },
        "sendHeaders": true,
        "headerParameters": {
          "parameters": [
            {
              "name": "Accept-Profile",
              "value": "public"
            }
          ]
        }
      },
      "alwaysOutputData": true
    },
    {
      "id": "cdcdcd9e-daeb-47ca-ab79-59b5ecd833b2",
      "name": "Upsert Checkout Event",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest",
      "typeVersion": 4.4,
      "position": [
        1060,
        300
      ],
      "parameters": {
        "method": "POST",
        "url": "https://yscegbszuckpdcopdszj.supabase.co/rest/v1/checkout_events",
        "authentication": "genericCredentialType",
        "genericAuthType": "httpHeaderAuth",
        "sendQuery": true,
        "queryParameters": {
          "parameters": [
